

Your position is important when used properly in conjunction 
with your skills and tactics. The effect of these varies 
depending on the combination. 

Stand   Standing is the best way to be able to attack.       
Rest    Regenerate hp/mp/sp faster. 
Sleep   Regenerate hp/mp/sp the fastest nonmagical way.
Sneak   This is often required to use or enhance rogue like skills.
Kneel   Kneeling allows the best sp regeneration and low hp/mp gains.
Fly     Reduced movement cost, access to more locations.

